From cmort Christopher Morton Subject Re AF ATS Red Army Fraction RAF communique As quoted from by Merth Eric William In article cmort Christopher Morton writes As quoted from by Phill Hallam Baker Isn't it wonderfull the way people can make the sadistic and indescriminate murder of the Bader Meinhof gang sound like altruism Gee Phil I'd remember where you are and that these people are monitoring the I'd also remember that they have about as much sense of humor as Ed It isn't Big Brother after all And all this time I thought that all those revolutionaries while blowing things up and killing the odd innocent person in the process really did love all us 'cause everybody knows that dialectical materialism will save you even if it has to get you killed first What a fool I've What you fail to see is that in order to make a nightmarish stew of psychosis and repression you have to break a few You the evil productive elements in society are those Damn the spirit full speed You're like a bunch of over educated New York jewish ACLU lawyers fighting to eliminate school prayer from the public schools in Arkansas Holly Silva